						tax brackets and rates set forth in paragraph (1) shall be replaced with the following:</div></i></font><font color="blue" class="blue_text"><i><table frame=""><tr><td><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:left; ; text-indent:0pt;">If the taxable income is:</div></td><td><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:left; hyphenation: yes;; text-indent:0pt;">The tax is:</div></td></tr><tr><td><div style="font-size:10pt; text-align:left; ; text-indent:0pt;">Not over $51,000 
